query:
SELECT
                            hash as "hash: _"
                            ,signer_address as "signer_address: _"
                            ,nonce as "nonce: _"
                            ,address_from as "address_from: _"
                            ,address_to as "address_to: _"
                            ,input as "input: _"
                            ,gas as "gas: _"
                            ,idx_in_block as "idx_in_block: _"
                            ,block_number as "block_number: _"
                            ,block_hash as "block_hash: _"
                        FROM transactions
                        WHERE hash = $1
